#: {{syn|fr|à en juger par}}

====Usage notes====
* In his work on French pronunciation, Pierre Fouché indicates that phonological {{m|fr|liaison}} is not made between the adverb {{m|fr|après}} and a subsequent vowel-initial word, but that {{m|fr||liaison}} ''is'' optionally made when such word follows a prepositional use of {{m|fr|après}} or the prepositive locution '''{{m|fr||d'après}}'''.<ref> {{cite-book|fr|author=Pierre Fouché|title=Traité de prononciation française|year=1959|pages=462, 477|isbn=9782252026106}}</ref>
